        },
        "is_private": false
      },
      "filename": "https://a-us.storyblok.com/f/1016915/1200x800/e71baa3be1/jesus-on-donkey-palm-sunday.jpg"
    },
    "title": "",
    "author": "93d238ee-eaa2-455c-9a29-5ca298395a20",
    "public": false,
    "content": {
      "type": "doc",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": null
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "They hailed him King as he passed by, ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "They strewed their garments in the road, ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "But they were set on earthly things, ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "And he on God.",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": null
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "They sang his praise for that he did, ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "But gave his message little thought;",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "They could not see that their souls’ good ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "Was all he sought.",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": null
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "They could not understand why he, ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "With powers so vast at his command, ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "Should hesitate to claim their rights ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "And free the land.",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": null
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Their own concerns and this world’s hopes ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "Shut out the wonder of his news;",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "And we, with larger knowledge, ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "still His Way refuse.",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": null
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "He walks among us still, unseen, ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "And still points out the only way, ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "But we still follow other gods ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hard_break"
            },
            {
              "text": "And him betray.",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "textStyle",
                  "attrs": {
                    "color": "#000000"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": null
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": null
          }
        }
      ]
    },
